title: People Pleaser
description: Blossom neglects her promise to Bubbles when she takes on too many things leaving Buttercup and Bubbles to fend for themselves.

title: UG Christmas Special
description: Santa and Uncle Grandpa must work through their personal differences order to save Christmas.

title: The Powerpuff Girls: A Documentary/Girls Gone Mild
description: The Powerpuff Girls a Documentary: A film student attempts to do a documentary on the Powerpuff Girls and learns catching these superheroes at rest is harder than he thought./Girls Gone Mild: When Parents Against Powerpuffs tell the girls that their superheroics are becoming too imitable, the girls must hold back on fighting crime.

title: Banana Joe
description: Cuando el director Brown le asigna a Darwin la tarea de hacer el anuario escolar, Darwin comienza pidiéndole a Banana Joe, el payaso de la clase, una simple selfi para la portada. Pero con Banana Joe, las cosas nunca son tan simples.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Creature Feature
description: Craig finds himself being chased by a monster in the Creek that's straight out of the movies!

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Inaccion de Gracias
description: Llegó el Día de Acción de Gracias y los Titanes, hartos de las tradiciones normales, inventan una propia.

title: The Island
description: While trying to sail to Japan, the Baby Bears get stranded on an island. Luckily, they meet Dave and Karla, who help with survival on the island while looking for an escape.

title: In Dreams
description: Steven's dreams start broadcasting onto his bedroom TV.

title: It Grows
description: As everyone celebrates Valentino for growing his first facial hair, a jealous Vic resorts to magical methods to grow a mustache and compete for attention.

title: Second Christmas
description: The Titans trick Starfire into believing in second Christmas with second Santa.

title: Apple Thief
description: Finn and Jake are feeling peckish and only one thing can satisfy their hunger: Tree Trunks' world-famous apple pie!

title: The Sleeper Part 1
description: Despite finding shelter at MacCadam's, Hot Rod is frustrated with their lack of progress rescuing more bots from the Quintesson Loop.

title: Drilling Deep
description: At school, Aki struggles with the side effects of his newly replicated Drill Man schematics; later, as Mega Man, he learns to control his Fire Powers in thwarting Drill Man's assault on Skyraisers Inc.

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: Arcade Mania
description: Steven takes the Crystal Gems to Funland Arcade where Garnet learns the allure of video games.

title: The Trial Part 2
description: The botched rescue leaves Hot Rod captured by the Quintessons, and the rest of the team to deal with a new, unwelcome bot sprung from The Loop.

title: The Gilded Path
description: The headquarters to the resistance is breached and Lloyd scrambles to avoid capture. Meanwhile, the Ninja are caught by Heavy Metal, but find an unlikely ally.

title: The Potato
description: When Darwin has lunch with Idaho, he decides to stop eating potatoes in solidarity with his brotato. However, he finds his obsession with his favourite food harder to kick than he ever imagined so Gumball decides to help his friend curb his carb cravings.

title: Three Gems and a Baby
description: Greg tells Steven the story of his first winter with Steven.

title: Have I Got a Deal for You
description: Ben and Rook must stop a giant rampaging alien from destroying Bellwood while dealing with a peace-loving alien-rights activist who doesn't want it hurt. (Introducing Hokestar, Solid Plugg 1st appearance, Pax, Sunder.)

title: Pancake's Bus Tour
description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

title: The More You Moe, the Moe You Know
description: Moe visits the tree house with a special birthday surprise for BMO. While BMO's mission stands on the brink of disaster, Finn & Jake host a strange guest.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: Crece
description: Mientras todo el mundo celebra a Valentino porque le creció su primer vello facial, Vic se pone celoso y recurre a métodos mágicos para dejarse crecer el bigote y competir por la atención.

title: A New Don
description: When Vic & Val discover that Don isn't really himself, it's up to them to use his kooky codex of conspiracies to save him.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Black Friday
description: Starfire is visited by three ghosts and shown the true meaning of Black Friday.

title: Una Leccion para Todos
description: Los Fantásticos le enseñan a unos chicos del vecindario a no imitar a los demás. Por ejemplo, a quienes utilizan a sus Bakugan con fines frívolos.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Craig and the Kid's Table
description: It's a Williams Family Thanksgiving, which means it's time to reunite The Kid's Table! But when Bernard accidentally destroys dessert, Craig uses the power of the Kids Table to help save his brother from certain grounding.

title: Pegatrix
description: Lia no concuerda con las técnicas de Pegatrix, pero durante una intensa batalla, debe aprender a confiar en los conocimientos de su Bakugan.

title: El es el Sheriff
description: iEl trío lucha por deshacerse del Rey cuando los acompaña como nuevo ayudante del sheriff por un día!

title: Luces Brillantes, Corazones Oscuros
description: Ben, Gwen y Max hacen una parada en el cementerio falso en el que se filma el programa de televisión favorito de Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre que su protagonista, Michael Morningstar, es un vampiro de la energía, se transforma en alienígena para mostrarle al mundo quién es la verdadera estrella del programa: Fuego.

title: Snow Month
description: After a snow day saves Blossom from having to face a boy who's asked her out, she decides to use her ice breath to keep it going even if that means plunging Townsville into eternal winter complete with monstrous yetis!

title: Together Forever
description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

title: Thanksgetting
description: It's Thanksgiving but the Titans are sick of the normal traditions so they create their own.

title: Ninjago Confidential
description: Back in Ninjago City, Zane and Pixal hit the mean streets to track down Milton Dyer, only to discover that things are not what they seem.

title: Mr. Universe
description: Greg takes Steven on the road to find the origins of the Universe name.

title: 'Twas the Fight Before Christmas
description: When Princess Morbucks tries to ruin Christmas for the children of the world, the Powerpuff Girls must save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Chill Out
description: Uncle Grandpa takes a kid to the North Pole for an epic snowball battle.

title: Mo' Linguish/Oops, I Did It Again
description: Mo' Linguish: Mojo is sentenced to do community service for Townsville and begins teaching English at the Learning Annex. Soon everyone is speaking in circles like Mojo and the town comes to a standstill./Oops, I Did It Again: When the Professor realizes that all his successful experiments are actually just accidents, he sets out to do something brilliant on purpose!

title: The Gauntlet Part 1
description: Lord Obsidian unites the Robot Masters against Mega Man and his family for an epic showdown at the Lighthouse.

title: Fideito
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben seguir teniendo la onda suficiente para aparecer en el video musical de su rapero favorito.

title: Burger Run/Monkey See, Monkey Don't
description: Burger Run: When the local Burger Joint is being threatened by a rogue Bakugan, Dan steps up to save the day and the burgers!/Monkey See, Monkey Don't: The AO stop neighborhood kids from copycat behavior (namely, using their Bakugan for frivolous reasons).

title: Suitable Armor
description: A veteran warrior insists that Vambre is under dressed for battle and takes it upon herself to garb Vambre in armor as Prohyas fights the beast solo without armor.

title: Ben 24hrs
description: When Ben (and Gwen!) attempt to stay up all night for Adrenaland, the only theme park open 24/7, he not only fails to utilize his alien powers to stay awake, but his "sleep-alien-ing" causes disaster after disaster that Gwen must fix before things get way out of hand.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

title: Duncan Carving
description: Duncan takes advantage of a questionable Halloween legend to steal candy from his classmates.

title: No Day Like Snow Day
description: When a blizzard hits the town, Master Frown tries to ruin everyone's fun by pretending to be a magical snowman! But when he gets frozen inside, Master Frown must worry less about ruining everyone's good time and instead not turning into a Frown-sicle, while he's forced to experience the joys of the holiday season!

title: Hot Dog Estrena su Pelicula
description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

title: Todo Por Mao Mismo
description: El deseo de Mao Mao de convertirse en leyenda lo lleva a querer superarse a sí mismo una y otra vez. ¿Pero cuánto es suficiente?

title: Chadsgiving
description: Clarence is excited for Thanksgiving Dinner with Chad's parents, but Chad is worried that their unusually laid back demeanor and bizarre customs will make him look irresponsible by association.

title: Curses/Bang for Your Buck
description: Curses: When Bubbles overhears the Professor saying some bad words, the girls add a whole new slew of adjectives to their vocabulary./Bang for Your Buck: When the girls and the Gangreen Gang discover a destructo ray for sale at Mojo's Yard Sale, each team sets out to see who can earn the most money and buy it first.

title: Pequeno
description: El legendario, gigantesco y crítico padre de Mao Mao visita a su hijo en su nuevo trabajo como sheriff.

title: Throwing Shade Part 2
description: Mega Man stops Fire Man by replicating his powers and fighting fire with fire. Unfortunately, Mega Man also learns that he can replicate a robot's mental state as well, and must get his own anger under control to win. Defeated, Fire Man reports back to his secret master, Sgt. Night!

title: Un dia nevado
description: Cuando una tormenta de nieve llega a la ciudad, Master Frown trata de arruinar la diversión de todos fingiendo ser un muñeco de nieve mágico. Pero cuando se congela por dentro, Master Frown debe preocuparse menos por arruinar la diversión de todos y más por no convertirse en un témpano malhumorado, imientras se ve obligado a experimentar la alegría de la temporada navideña!

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 2
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Perfect Tree
description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

title: Merry Christmas Mordecai
description: Mordecai has to get through a Christmas party with C.J. without messing everything up.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: Boss For a Day
description: When Chata lets Vic be the boss of the taco stand for the day Vic decides to fire Val, which has disastrous consequences.

title: Sale el Don
description: Cuando Vic y Val descubren que Don Jalapeño no es realmente él mismo, depende de ellos usar el alocado libro de conspiraciones de Don para salvarlo.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: El Arbol Perfecto
description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

title: Christmas Parties
description: The Bears have been invited to all their friends' Christmas parties. In an effort to have time to crash Nom Nom's huge star-studded bash, the Bears first try to make quick stops at all their friends' parties throughout the night.

title: Small
description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Whatever Happened to... Rippy Roo?
description: Rippy Roo visits the plaza.

title: Bismuto Casual
description: Perla invita a Bismuto a la pista de patinaje para darle una lección sobre cómo forjar relaciones humanas.

title: Safari Joe
description: While minding her own business, Cheetara is caught in a trap set by Safari Joe, the famously annoying hunter! After escaping, she rallies the other ThunderCats to help her stop Joe once and for all, by turning the tables and capturing him!

title: Un Almuerzo Inesperado
description: Cuando el Restaurante de Hamburguesas es amenazado por un violento Bakugan, Dan llega para salvar el día...y las hamburguesas.

title: Manzana, Concentrate
description: Manzana ayuda a Cebollín a cumplir su sueño de competir en un programa de pastelería.

title: Company Man
description: When Clarence loses the ball during a soccer game, he ends up following it into an office building, where he's mistaken for the boss's kid and given free reign to wander around. Will he climb his way to the top of the corporate ladder or end up on the chopping block?

title: The Gift
description: The girls must replace the Professor's Christmas present on Christmas Eve.

title: Apple's in Trouble
description: Apple is challenged to a fight by a grumpy Cheesesteak, so he and Onion go on a quest to find the source of Cheesesteak's grumpiness.

title: The Prodigal Father
description: Zane, kidnapped by the Mechanic, faces Unagami. Master Wu fights to free Zane, while Pixal questions Milton Dyer for information on how to shut down Prime Empire.

title: Firstbourne
description: Emperor Garmadon has taken control of Ninjago City where Lloyd retreats to the shadows. Meanwhile, the other Ninja and Young Wu are shipwrecked in the Realm of Oni & Dragon and find they are not alone.

title: Bright Lights, Black Hearts
description: Ben, Gwen, and Max stop by the graveyard set of Gwen's favorite TV show, The Unalivers, but when Ben discovers its lead, Michael Morningstar, is an energy vampire he goes alien to show the world the real star of the show: Heatblast.

title: Giant Woman
description: During a mission to the Sky Spire, Steven tries to convince Amethyst and Pearl to fuse together and become a giant woman.

title: Secret Santa
description: When Uncle Grandpa and the crew all have the same popular and hard-to-find gift in mine for their Secret Santa, their nice Christmas shopping trip to the mall turns into a crazy competition.

title: Growing Pains
description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

title: Superman's Pal, Sid Sharp
description: When obnoxious reporter Sid Sharp decides that Clark Kent is getting all his stories because of his connection to Superman, Sid decides to become his own superhero to out scoop him.

title: King of Camping
description: The Williams Family goes camping and Craig helps his dad prove he's the King of Camping.

title: Thanksgiving
description: When Raven's father Trigon shows up for Thanksgiving dinner, Robin's seating plan isn't the only thing that gets ruined.

title: Merry Christmas
description: When the Rustbucket's A/C goes on the fritz in the middle of the desert, Ben, Max and Gwen take refuge at Holiday Village, an over the top Christmas theme park that seems to appear out of nowhere. The place is run by an evil entity known as Mr. Jingles, who takes Max prisoner because he believes Max is Santa! It's up to Ben and Gwen to free Max and break the spell Mr. Jingles has cast on Holiday Village, freeing others who've been trapped their for years and releasing the theme park.

title: Holly Jolly Secrets Part 1
description: Finn and Jake continue to explore the world of old Christmas specials while the Ice King fumes.

title: The Citizen Part 1
description: Hot Rod, Clobber, Dead End, and Whirl search the long-buried Titan for MacCadam and anything to help them defeat the Quintessons.

title: Ben 24 Horas
description: Cuando Ben (iy Gwen!) intenta quedarse despierto toda la noche para ir a Adrenaland -el único parque temático abierto las 24 horas, los siete días de la semana- no solo es incapaz de utilizar sus poderes alienígenas para lograr su objetivo, sino que además su estado de adormecimiento alienígena provoca un desastre tras otro, y Gwen debe arreglar las cosas antes de que todo se salga de control.

title: Pizza Eve
description: Uncle Grandpa falls for Pizza Steve's "girlfriend" and ends up in serious danger.

title: Lista de Traviesos
description: Es Nochebuena y Brock está emocionado por la visita de Santa Claus. Mientras se prepara para que Master Frown le lea un cuento para dormir, Unikitty y la banda irrumpen en su casa. Están ahí para evitar que Master Frown arruine más Navidades. Frown se declara inocente, pero Unikitty y la banda cuentan las historias de las Navidades pasadas que ya arruinó. ¿Frown probará su inocencia o se pondrá a la cabeza de la lista de los traviesos?

title: The Final Countdown
description: Rook and his little Plumbers must defend the Base from a mysterious lockdown.

title: Bromas Pesadas
description: Las constantes bromas pesadas de Wynton colman la paciencia de su Bakugan, Trox, quien decide darle una lección.

title: Stop, Drop and Side Scroll
description: Our ninja barely have time to mourn the loss of their fallen ninja friends before being thrust into the madness of Terra Domina where Lloyd will have to face an old adversary from his past.

title: The Thanksgiving Special
description: The park guys need to get Thanksgiving dinner for their families to save Thanksgiving.

title: Collection Infection
description: Having pared down their Magisword collection, the Warriors are forced into unconventional battle choices on a dangerous mission into the Deepest Darkest Woods.

title: Afterschool Snackdown
description: Craig enters a food competition in the Creek but worries he may be out of his league.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Tu Ba or Not Tu Ba
description: The class tries to help Chef achieve his dream of joining the world's most famous Tuba Band, Tubalicious, only to regret it when they realize how much they'll miss him.

title: Meet Tygra
description: The smartest Thundercat, Tygra. Tygra's mission is to make Lion-O a better leader. He might get around to it too, if he wasn't so busy cleaning up after the other Thundercats.

title: So Many Birthdays
description: So Many Birthdays: Steven learns that the Crystal Gems are thousands of years old and decides to make up for all the thousands of birthdays they've missed.

title: Sr. Universo
description: Greg lleva a Steven de viaje para encontrar los orígenes del nombre del Universo.

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Speedway Five-Billion
description: Unagami's soldiers, the Red Visors, finally discover the secret location of Scott's garage and attack the ninja, who manage to escape with the help of Racer Seven, and enter the spectacular Speedway Five Billion.

title: The Birthday to End All Birthdays Part 1
description: Unikitty and the gang secretly throw Master Frown the birthday of his dreams, but their efforts have lasting repercussions beyond Frown's special day.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: Lucha de Pulgares
description: El trío decide concursar en la competencia anual de Lucha de Pulgares, pero una sorpresa obliga a Mao Mao a lidiar con algo impensado… la derrota.

title: Roughing It Up/What's the Big Idea?
description: Roughing It Up: The girls and the Professor set out on an old-fashioned vacation to the Townsville Swamp. Trouble is, Fuzzy and his nephews are there, too./What's the Big Idea?: 20 story high Powerpuff Girls spell disaster for Townsville when they delicately try to stop Mojo from taking over.

title: Duele Crecer
description: Steven va al médico por primera vez.

title: Radio Ninjago libre
description: Lloyd deberá encontrar su voz mientras lidera una pequeña resistencia para capturar las señales de transmisión en Ciudad Ninjago. Mientras tanto en el Primer Reino, el Barón de Hierro lleva a los Ninjas en una cacería de dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Dude Where's Macaw
description: While trying to defend his elite gamer status Chef uses an old cheat code that brings a dangerous avatar to life.

title: Field Trippin'
description: After a pit stop bathroom break during a school field trip, Clarence returns to the parking lot and accidentally gets on the wrong school bus - which takes him to a different school!

title: The Brain Buster
description: A mysterious creature abducts Batman, Mr. Terrific, Luthor and two of the brainiest villains in the universe to put them to the test to discover who is the smartest among them.

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val le guarda rencor a Vic, lo cual atrae sin querer a un malvado cadejo, una bestia mitológica parecida a un lobo.

title: The K.O. Trap
description: KO, Rad, and Enid are caught in an especially devious trap.

title: Aventuras Cuidando Ninos
description: Ben, Gwen y Max se encuentran con una familia que parece ser un reflejo de ellos. Pero cuando Max sale a caminar con su matriarca, Maxine, Ben se ve obligado a cuidar a Simon Sez, un malcriado con una mochila diseñada por Billy Billones, que lo convierte en un robot formidable.

title: New Year's Kiss
description: Rigby has to stop Mordecai from kissing a girl on New Year's Eve.

title: Lil Noodle
description: Apple and Onion must remain legit enough to be in their favorite rapper's music video.

title: Thumb War
description: The gang decide to compete in the annual Thumb War competition, but a surprise forces Mao Mao to deal with the unthinkable... losing.

title: Winter Forecast
description: Steven has to get Connie home before it snows.

title: Top of the Naughty List
description: It's Christmas Eve and Brock is excited for Santa to come and visit as he settles down for a bedtime story from Master Frown, Unikitty and gang burst in. They are there to stop Master Frown from ruining any more Christmases. Frown pleads innocent but Unikitty and the gang tell the stories of the past Christmases he has already ruined.  Will Frown prove his innocence or will he rocket to the top of the Naughty List?

title: Tummy Trouble
description: When the Incursean armada kidnaps the Gourmand Queen, Ben and Rook must get the warring Gormand factions to work together to save her and stop the Incursean invasion.

title: Frenemies/Strata's Fear
description: Frenemies: Two new Bakugan Brawlers, Shun and Magnus, try out for the AO./Strata's Fear: The AO solve the mystery of a kid's missing Bakugan and meet a Bakugan Hunter named Strata.

title: The Sleeper Part 2
description: Hot Rod desperately tries to free Optimus from the Loop while Perceptor and Dead End investigate why MacCadam's is hidden from Quintesson attention.

title: Manzana esta en Problemas
description: Bistec con Queso, malhumorado, desafía a Manzana a una pelea. De ese modo, Manzana puede embarcarse con Cebollín en una misión para encontrar el origen del malhumor de Bistec con Queso.

title: Apple's Focus
description: Apple helps Onion achieve his dream of competing on a baking show.

title: Growing Pains
description: Puppycorn is sick of Unikitty always helping him out and doesn't want to be the "little" brother anymore, so he uses some of Dr Fox's 'grow taffy' to grow literally bigger than Unikitty. Meanwhile, a black hole is on its way to destroy the planet. But when Puppycorn takes too much and continues growing, he starts accidentally destroying the kingdom. Unikitty takes grow taffy and grows big as well to help out, but when they're both the size of planets, Puppycorn proves he can take care of himself on his own by destroying the black hole and saving the kingdom.

title: Super Black Friday
description: After being forced to work on a holiday, KO, Rad and Enid take a stand.

title: El Miedo de Strata
description: Los Fantásticos resuelven la misteriosa desaparición del Bakugan de un niño, y conocen a un cazador de Bakugan llamado Strata.

title: Summer Fun Day!
description: The Thundercats are exhausted from fighting bad guys all the time so Lion-O suggests they spend a relaxing summer fun day at the beach, with no fighting! Unfortunately the beach is home to the Crabmen, giant, clawed humanoids that fight anyone who steps on their sand! Looks like summer fun day might involve some fighting!

title: Let's Get Shadowy
description: KO teams up with an unlikely ally to take on an old foe.

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: The Citizen Part 2
description: Joined by Perceptor, the ragtag team discover the dormant Titan is far more dangerous than they expected.

title: All By Mao Self
description: Mao Mao's desire to be a legend drives him to keep topping himself. But how much is enough?

title: Hibernacion
description: Por ser un grupo urbano, los Osos jamás escucharon hablar de la idea de hibernar, hasta que Chloe les cuenta al respecto. Pardo, a quien le encanta la idea de comer mucho y luego dormir todo lo que se le dé la gana, se entrega a la hibernación sin pensarlo. Pero está tan entusiasmado con la idea de hibernar... que no se puede dormir.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Colosal adopta a un monstruo abandonado, pero es mejor dejar algunas cosas en estado salvaje.

title: Don't Laze Me, Bro
description: Ben and his arch-enemy Billy Billions clash in a duel for supremacy at the world's largest Laser Tag Park, LASER TOWN. But, when Billy inadvertently ignites a robot rebellion, and the lasers are set from tag to disintegrate, their childish game escalates into a full blown war! The two foes find that they must set aside their petty differences and team up in order to make it out alive, let alone save the day!

title: El Bravucon
description: Los Fantásticos deben lidiar con un bravucón que usa a su Bakugan para intimidar a los chicos del vecindario.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Bring on the Bad Guys
description: Axel, Zoe, and the team confront Madcap and his minions as they terrorize a local supermarket.

title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 1
description: Dan conoce a su pareja Bakugan, Drago, por primera vez y nos enteramos del "incidente" que ocurrió en la Tierra hace doce años.

title: Christmas Movies
description: On Christmas Eve, the Baby Bears defend a video store from getting robbed.

title: En Suenos
description: Los sueños de Steven comienzan a transmitirse en el televisor de su dormitorio.

title: Way Back Wendel
description: Courtney must deliberately lose a challenge or let the entire world go back in time. It's a really hard choice for her.

title: Juntos por Siempre
description: Connie tiene una visión muy clara de su futuro, y Steven quiere asegurarse de ser parte de esa visión.

title: Snow Tubing
description: Rigby wants Eileen to go snow tubing.

title: How to Build a Dragon
description: While Lloyd and the rebels celebrate their successful strike against Emperor Garmadon, in the Realm of Oni and Dragon, the Ninja dare an elaborate escape from the clutches of Iron Baron and his Dragon Hunters.

title: Dolores del crecimiento
description: Perricornio está cansado de que Unikitty siempre lo ayude y ya no quiere ser el hermano pequeño, así que usa un poco del dulce de crecimiento de la Dra. Fox para ser más grande que Unikitty.

title: The Great Spaghetti Western
description: Mr. Gus repeatedly runs afoul of a crooked mayor while winning the hears of the townsfolk.

title: Spies Like Us
description: Uncle Andrew warns Axel that his vintage "Agent Danger" action figure is off-limits, only to have the toy escape on its own! Axel and the team must return Danger to its rightful place before Uncle Andrew finds out.

title: The True Meaning of Christmas
description: Fed up with never getting presents from Santa, the Titans head to the north pole to take themselves off the Naughty List by any means necessary.

title: Jefe por un dia
description: Cuando Chata deja que Vic sea el jefe del puesto de tacos por un día, él decide despedir a Val, lo que trae consecuencias desastrosas.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin necesita encontrar una foto de Clayton para ponerla en la portada del anuario escolar... ipero comete el error de pedirle ayuda de Tobías, que está interesado en aparecer en la portada!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Meet The Thunderkittens
description: The Thunderkittens might be the youngest Thundercats, but Wilykit and Wilykat are a dynamic brother and sister duo! They'll help take down any foe, even if they don't really know what their own capsule weapons can do.

title: #ItsComplicated
description: When Hal Jordan sees Carol Ferris with a new boyfriend, his ego can't handle the rejection, resulting in the most absurd Lantern battle ever.

title: Maestros
description: Cuando Darwin les pregunta a sus amigos qué profesor merece estar en la portada del anuario, iles cuesta encontrar a un solo candidato digno!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Local Heroes/Pegatrix
description: Local Heroes: After the AO cause accidental destruction Dan's parents question whether the kids should be allowed to keep their Bakugan./Pegatrix: Lia disagrees with her new Bakugan Pegatrix on battle techniques but during a fierce fight Lia must rely on Pegatrix's battle savy.

title: They Lurk Below
description: Max's old friend has built the world's only underwater resort, and Ben, Gwen and Max are invited for a sneak peak. But it turns out in order to power the resort, Max's friend took an energy orb from a race of underwater aliens. Now, the aliens want their energy orb back and destroy the resort in order to get it.

title: Ghoul Spirit
description: Gwen rejects the friendship of a friendly ghost.

title: He's the Sheriff
description: The gang struggles to get rid of the King when he joins them as their new deputy-for-a-day!

title: Vote Gumball…and Bobert?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He turns his attention to Bobert, the school's electronic wonderkid - but does Gumball really fit into his equation? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Bismuth Casual
description: Pearl invites Bismuth to the roller rink for a lesson on how to forge human relationships.

title: Hierro y piedra
description: Cole y Wu Joven intentan liberar a sus amigos, que han sido capturados por una tribu de Cazadores de Dragones. Mientras tanto en Ninjago, Lloyd se reúne con unos viejos amigos que quizás sean aliados valiosos contra el Emperador Garmadon.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: The Temple of Madness
description: Jay must stand alone against Unagami in the end-game, yet Unagami has a bigger battle in facing the truth about his own identity.

title: Somewhere Over the Swingset
description: When the girls disobey the Professor and swing all the way over the swing set, they must deal with unexpected consequences.

title: Stuck on You
description: Kybher, aided by a booger-like slime biot named Skurd, attacks Ben & co, but the tables turn when Skurd gloms onto Ben!

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Escuela De Payasos
description: Mientras Ben disfruta en el estacionamiento a la salida de un partido de fútbol americano de ex estudiantes de la Universidad de State, se alía con los antiguos compañeros del Abuelo Max para impedir que Zombozo, un payaso demente, le robe a todo el público durante el entretiempo.

title: Stray Bullet
description: In order to save an innocent squirrel, Bubbles gives him a dash of Chemical X, giving him some super squirrel powers.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin se propone encontrar una foto de Carrie para la portada del anuario escolar, pero ambos terminan recordando todas sus travesuras espeluznantes del pasado.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Birthday to End All Birthdays Part 2
description: Following the events of Master Frown's birthday, Unikitty and her friends form a resistance group to restore the Unikingdom.

title: The Trial Part 1
description: To awaken the Titan Iaconus, Hot Rod plans a daring rescue of the Autobot's only City Speaker.

title: White Elephant Gift Exchange
description: The park guys want revenge on Muscle Man for all his terrible gifts.

title: Super Dia de Ofertas
description: Cuando los obligan a trabajar en un día festivo, KO, Rad y Enid se pronuncian en contra de la medida.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: You're a Good Man, Mojo Jojo
description: The holidays are Mojo's favorite time…for ruining everything! But this year, he may just learn the reason for the season.

title: El Origen de las Especies Parte 2
description: Dan y sus amigos ganan la Batalla Bakugan, demostrando que los Fantásticos son nuestros héroes y los mejores Peleadores Bakugan.

title: Rustbucket RIP
description: During a tour of historic Oldeville Ben finds a rare Sumo Slammers card, but when Billy Billions comes to claim the same card Ben has to battle Billy's high-tech drones which have hijacked the Rust Bucket!

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: El camino dorado
description: El cuartel general de la resistencia es irrumpido y Lloyd lucha por no ser capturado. Mientras tanto, los Ninjas son capturados por Heavy-Metal, pero encuentran un aliado improbable.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Rebelion En La Granja
description: Ben encuentra el laboratorio secreto del Doctor Ánimo -ahora gobernado por los alfas, sus mutantes superiores- y debe ayudar a los animales inferiores mientras está atrapado en forma de Insectoide.

title: Ene-Amigos
description: Dos nuevos Peleadores Bakugan, Shun y Magnus, buscan ser parte de Los Fantásticos.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin le pide a Sarah una foto para poner en la portada del anuario escolar. Pero cuando Sarah trata de ayudar, las cosas se complican un poco.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Los Cadejos
description: Val holds a grudge against Vic, unwittingly attracting an evil cadejo, a mythological wolf-like beast.

title: Freaky Gwen Ben
description: When Ben interferes with malicious magician Hex's quest for the earth-moving Titan Gloves at a swap meet, he inadvertently switches bodies with Gwen forcing him to walk a mile in her shoes and vice-versa!

title: Como construir un dragon
description: Mientras Lloyd y los rebeldes celebran su exitoso golpe contra el Emperador Garmadon, en el Reino de Oni y Dragón, los Ninjas se aventuran con un elaborado escape de las garras del Barón de Hierro y sus Cazadores de Dragones.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Unleashed
description: While the Justice League is away on a mission, Plastic Man is not only left in charge of the Watchtower, but also Superman's dog, Krypto.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: Descanse En Paz Rustbucket
description: Durante un tour por la histórica ciudad de Oldeville, Ben encuentra una carta de Sumo Slammers poco común. Pero cuando Billy Billones reclama esa carta, Ben debe luchar contra los drones tecnológicos de Billy, ique secuestraron la Chatarra!

title: Origin of Species
description: Origin of Species, Part 1: Dan meets his partner Bakugan Drago for the first time and we learn about the incident that happened on Earth twelve years ago./Origin of Species, Part 2: Dan and friends win the Bakugan Battle, firmly establishing the Awesome Ones as our heroes and Bakugan Brawlers.

title: Craig y la mesa de los ninos
description: Llegó el Día de Acción de Gracias de la familia Williams, iasí que es hora de reunir a la Mesa de los chicos! Pero cuando, por accidente, Bernard destruye el postre, Craig usa el poder de la Mesa de los chicos como ayuda para salvar a su hermano de un castigo asegurado.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Vote Gumball…and Leslie?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He hopes Leslie's newfound cheer-team fame will elevate his campaign, but Leslie won't play ball. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Trouble Helix
description: Flashback episode: Young Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max visit Azmuth on Galvan Prime. There, they have their first encounter with Malware, a corrupted Mechamorph who's determined to make Azmuth cure him, by any means!

title: For the Love of Narwhal
description: Vambre rejects Darlin' Narwhal Magisword as being unfit for battle, but when Prohyas trains and brings out its full potential, Vambre resorts to improper extremes to get it back.

title: Heroes Locales
description: Los Fantásticos provocan una ola de destrucción por accidente, y los padres de Dan se preguntan si deberían permitirle a los niños conservar sus Bakugan.

title: Gwen O Ben
description: Cuando Ben interfiere con la misión de Hex -el mago malicioso- para los Titan Gloves, que hacen tareas de movimiento de tierra en un centro de trueque, Hex intercambia el cuerpo de Ben con el de Gwen, lo cual lo obliga a caminar un kilómetro y medio en sus zapatos iy viceversa!

title: Vote Gumball…and Anyone?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. He is running out of options - will anybody, or anything, be his vice president? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Barehanded
description: When Green Lantern leaves his ring in an intergalactic restroom after washing his hands, he discovers it's gone, leading him on a wild chase for the aliens who might have taken it.

title: #NoDerribenElArbol
description: Jessica Cruz y Pam Isley se unen para evitar que un antiguo árbol sea talado, pero ninguna se da cuenta de quien es el alter ego de la otra ni los extremos a los que llegarán para proteger lo que es importante.
originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

title: Peliculas Navidenas
description: En Nochebuena, los Osos bebé impiden un robo en una tienda de videos.

title: Primogenita
description: El Emperador Garmadon ha tomado el control de Ciudad Ninjago donde Lloyd se retira hacia las sombras. Mientras tanto, los otros Ninjas y Wu Joven quedan varados en el Reino de Oni y Dragón y descubren que no están solos.
originalseriesname: Ninjago: Masters of Spinjitzu en Espanol

title: Alan
description: Darwin quiere poner a Alan en la portada del anuario escolar, pero la aparente modestia de Alan se interpone.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: No Me Ataques, Amigo
description: Ben y Billy Billones, su archienemigo, se enfrentan en un duelo por la supremacía en Laser Town, el parque de simulación de armas láser. Pero cuando, sin darse cuenta, Billy desata una rebelión robótica, y los lásers pasan de tocar a desintegrar, isu juego infantil se convierte en una guerra sin cuartel! Los enemigos descubren que deben dejar de lado sus diferencias y unirse para poder salir con vida...iy salvar al resto del planeta!

title: Party Animal
description: Green Arrow, who is determined to finally throw a successful holiday party for the Justice League, finds his plans thwarted when Plastic Man brings a tranquilized super villain to the gathering.

title: Fall Anthology
description: In an attempt to finish a school project, Craig remembers some of his favorite Fall moments.

title: Cuddle Monster
description: After being told by Chata that they can't get a pet, Vic & Val adopt a wild lizard, unaware of its magical properties, and decide to keep it secret from Chata.

title: Radio Free NinjaGo
description: Lloyd must find his voice as he leads a small resistance to capture the airwaves in Ninjago City. Meanwhile in the First Realm, Iron Baron takes the Ninja on a dragon hunt.

title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

title: Ice Cream Hunt
description: Clarence enlists the help of his eccentric neighbor Larry to take the trio out for ice cream and the ride of their lives!

title: The Gauntlet Part 2
description: As Dr. Light and Suna turn the Robot Masters against each other, Mega Man defeats and unmasks his arch nemeses, Lord Obsidian, who turns out to be Sgt. Night in disguise, and finally learns the identity of Namagem, Mega Man's long lost twin brother!

title: Throwing Shade Part 1
description: Sgt. Night publicly criticizes Dr. Light's views on human & robot unity during a school assembly, invoking the ire of Fire Man and forcing Silicon City's newly minted hero, Mega Man, to intervene.

title: #SchoolGhoul
description: When Tatsu Yamashiro asks for help at a haunted all-girls academy, Barbara Gordon and Kara Danvers find themselves caught up in something much bigger than a ghost hunt.

title: Thank You
description: The Snow Golem and his beseeching pup pay a visit to the Fire Kingdom.

title: Nueva Mascota
description: Después de que Chata les dijera que no pueden tener una mascota, Vic y Val adoptan un lagarto salvaje, sin conocer sus propiedades mágicas, y deciden mantenerlo en secreto para que Chata no se entere.

title: Iron & Stone
description: Cole and Young Wu attempt to free their friends, who have been taken captive by a tribe of Dragon Hunters. Meanwhile in Ninjago, Lloyd is reunited with some old friends who may prove valuable allies against Emperor Garmadon.

title: Bully for You/Trolling for Laughs
description: Bully for You: The AO must handle a neighborhood bully who is using his Bakugan to pick on the local kids./Trolling for Laughs: Wynton's constant practical jokes wear thin on his Bakugan Trox so the Bakugan decide to teach him a lesson.
